%%EOF

% The visible report has deliberate line wrapping and page numbering.
% The refactoring keeps Bank as a coordinator rather than a domain-data owner.
% Account owns balance changes because balance and interest rate are account state.
% Branch owns staff transfer because the staff collection belongs to the branch.
% Customer owns contact details because address and phone number describe customers.
% Payroll owns pay schedule updates to remove navigation through internal objects.
% The client assertions were preserved and redirected to the objects that own state.
% The regression suite verifies that behaviour remains stable after redistribution.
% The visible report has deliberate line wrapping and page numbering.
% The refactoring keeps Bank as a coordinator rather than a domain-data owner.